<subSubSection id="A71CEC7C72F43BCC7411634B935026F9" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" type="distribution and taxonomic notes">
<paragraph id="3EF3C04FF2F6BD7A50060E86AA3FF65B" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">Distribution and taxonomic notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="54682FDEDD3E176F1ABC0AA35EEBC907" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">
Based on a description by 
<bibRefCitation id="D2D958AD6B53F531F76FF392F2B8CE46" author="Oberthuer, C" journalOrPublisher="Etudes de Lepidopterologie comparee" pageId="8" pageNumber="131" refId="B28" refString="Oberthuer, C, 1910. . Etudes de Lepidopterologie comparee 4" volume="4" year="1910">
<normalizedToken id="4690EB482B1B46158F9ED02445866B44" originalValue="Oberthür">Oberthuer</normalizedToken>
(1910
</bibRefCitation>
: 591), Verity provided the name 
<taxonomicName id="2DBEA851356F5A5384C99CCFCB588EAF" authorityName="Verity" authorityYear="1920" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="subsp. pyrenaea" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="pyrenaea">
<emphasis id="FA9AEFD0B748EB21834CF0016B5CEBF7" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">pyrenaea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for the population of 
<taxonomicName id="FBBAA34DFB352D264A4E6AB636F3217D" baseAuthorityName="Esper" baseAuthorityYear="1789" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhadamanthus">
<emphasis id="5662ADF064C7E10B2C69483676B079E1" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">Zygaena rhadamanthus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
occurring at La Trancada 
<normalizedToken id="9E88A5368DEFBFE7C112B0FC76D06022" originalValue="d’Ambouilla">d'Ambouilla</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="32FBD1298366B1E1A42EEFC63F3D2FC9" originalValue="Pyrénées-Orientales">Pyrenees-Orientales</normalizedToken>
, between Prades and Mont Canigou). 
<bibRefCitation id="8B9FA6831297800212C6D5BC0F2CF6E7" author="Leraut, P" journalOrPublisher="NAP Editions, Verrieres-le Buisson" pageId="7" pageNumber="130" refId="B20" refString="Leraut, P, 2012. Volume 3: Moths of Europe, Zygaenids, Pyralids 1 and Brachodids. NAP Editions, Verrieres-le Buisson" title="Volume 3: Moths of Europe, Zygaenids, Pyralids 1 and Brachodids." year="2012">Leraut (2012</bibRefCitation>
: 98) considered this taxon to be a 'simple 
<normalizedToken id="DD03263C64A27029320430D52325659A" originalValue="synonym’">synonym'</normalizedToken>
of the nominotypical 
<taxonomicName id="D6077323BBBAF9BFFC0CD2A4B060F5D2" authority="rhadamanthus" authorityName="rhadamanthus (Esper" authorityYear="1789" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. rhadamanthus" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="rhadamanthus">
<emphasis id="BB08278826ABDC99FFB4388AEC452535" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">Zygaena rhadamanthus rhadamanthus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, a placement with which we agree even though 
<bibRefCitation id="CD794325B9C2B508673F10C036758502" author="Hofmann, A" journalOrPublisher="Harley Books, Colchester" pageId="7" pageNumber="130" refId="B17" refString="Hofmann, A, Tremewan, WG, 1996. A systematic Catalogue of the Zygaeninae (Lepidoptera: Zygaenidae). Harley Books, Colchester" title="A systematic Catalogue of the Zygaeninae (Lepidoptera: Zygaenidae)." year="1996">Hofmann and Tremewan (1996</bibRefCitation>
: 131) had considered it to be a valid subspecies with which the taxon 
<taxonomicName id="EE83F39AE74D5813C61342E6AECF449F" authorityName="Aistleitner" authorityYear="1990" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. boixolsis" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="boixolsis">
<emphasis id="6A4F6D4FA34695C4C010541C8D5D6485" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="127">Zygaena rhadamanthus boixolsis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Aistleitner, 1990, had been placed as a synonym. The latter is now automatically transferred as a synonym of the nominotypical subspecies. Specimens from La Trancada 
<normalizedToken id="DA239C6C8D45DFC7D94FF26DFF61311A" originalValue="d’Ambouilla">d'Ambouilla</normalizedToken>
lack the white scaling (griseoid) on the ground colour of the forewings; moreover, a red abdominal cingulum is absent, as found in the nominotypical subspecies.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
